{"3192260": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "與女僕一起生活", "steam_appid": 3192260, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/82cc9ee9df38ab9662ba24b8229fdc15.poster.avif?t=1774005224\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/82cc9ee9df38ab9662ba24b8229fdc15.webm?t=1774005224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/82cc9ee9df38ab9662ba24b8229fdc15.mp4?t=1774005224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✨ 故事大綱</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在父母因事故離世後，你過著孤單又空虛的日子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某天，一位神秘的女僕正蜷縮著睡在你的房門前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她自稱為了報答你，主動承擔起家中所有家務，煮飯、打掃、照顧生活起居樣樣包辦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沒有去處的她，請求能留下來與你一起生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >於是，一段既溫馨又有點不可告人的同居生活就此展開⋯⋯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被她全心全意照料的同時，你也能慢慢發現她隱藏的秘密：她與你那逐漸升溫的悸動與慾望。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/0b3da96ebbeae98d4226cab25c31cfd2.poster.avif?t=1774005224\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/0b3da96ebbeae98d4226cab25c31cfd2.webm?t=1774005224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/0b3da96ebbeae98d4226cab25c31cfd2.mp4?t=1774005224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 遊戲玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>這是一款以輕鬆互動為主的2D遊戲，實際遊玩體驗更接近模擬與女僕日常生活的視覺小說，</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過滑鼠操作簡單的遊戲介面，你可以進行與女僕聊天、泡茶、逛街、換裝等生活互動，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甚至可以從背後偷偷來一些色色的「小惡作劇」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著你與女僕相處的日子越來越多，培養的感情也越來越深，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在道晚安之後，說不定會有什麼色色的事情發生⋯⋯？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果很在意女僕的狀態，就去商店購買能夠檢視女僕內心的神祕道具，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看看她目前的開發度與性慾指數。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/cbb546555caf27ca873be4f9e3bd6a5f.avif?t=1774005224\" width=1560 height=879 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「幫主人服務，也是女僕的義務之一。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受不了想要的話，就請她幫你服務⋯⋯？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要她換上裸體圍裙打掃家中，想偷襲她的你忍不住對她惡作劇的話，她會有什麼反應⋯⋯？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讓她欲求不滿好幾天，也許就能窺見她慾望的秘密⋯⋯？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/6187fc16267d6b4c90b7821b9a541e47.avif?t=1774005224\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras_big/6187fc16267d6b4c90b7821b9a541e47.webp?t=1774005224 width=1560 height=884 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在靠近她後可以用滑鼠點擊她敏感的地方，看看她的反應。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色色時可以選擇要放進去抽插或拔出來，要射在外面還是裡面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/30be79a4ba32661afe1bf55840621517.avif?t=1774005224\" width=1077 height=615 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲沒有明確結局，你可以一直與女僕的她共享屬於你們的親密時光，沉浸在她的溫柔陪伴裡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在陪伴女僕超過一定天數後，回憶將出現解鎖H場景的提示。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌟 角色介紹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/2b757c8c919cf6dbd89335ab3ede6443.avif?t=1774005224\" width=400 height=700 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >織笠 琴音 (CV：鳴森りいあ)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾在房門前被你「撿到」的神秘女僕，自稱是為了報答你，總是帶著溫柔的微笑，將家中打理得井井有條。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >料理、清掃、泡茶樣樣精通，對你的照顧更是無微不至。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她從未掩飾對你這位主人的好感，作為你的專屬女僕，她不只渴望照顧你的起居，更渴望照顧你寂寞的身心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >偶爾，她似乎會透露出對你早已熟悉的模樣⋯⋯究竟她的真實身分是？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💟紙娃娃換裝系統</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可在女僕商店購入各種服裝道具，讓她換上不同衣服之後跟她搭話的話，也許就能夠解鎖不同的色色場景喔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/14cb70b50affea333fb862b4e4123588.avif?t=1774005224\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras_big/14cb70b50affea333fb862b4e4123588.webp?t=1774005224 width=1560 height=817 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豐富的換裝系統，髮型、日常服、睡衣、內衣內褲及其他配件可更換，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過一百種排列組合，照主人你的心情與喜好為她搭配服裝吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💟 遊戲特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💗 超過一百種服裝搭配組合，隨心所欲換裝，打造屬於你的理想女僕<br>💗 遊玩時間 1-2hr<br>💗 9張HCG與豐富的表情服裝差分，從日常色色的貼心照顧到意想不到的甜蜜挑逗<br>💗 1280×720 的可愛 2D 畫面，溫馨又充滿幻想的宅邸時光<br>💗 回憶功能，可查看你與她珍貴的甜蜜色色回憶畫面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >準備好迎接只屬於你與女僕的甜蜜生活吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192260/extras/82cc9ee9df38ab9662ba24b8229fdc15.poster.avif?t=1774005224\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.st